premise_source_doc_sentence: The first season garnered an average of 9.47 million viewers per all 22 episodes in the U.S. Out of all regular primetime programming that aired during the 2005 -- 2006 American television season , How I Met Your Mother ranked 51st out of 156 , according to the Nielsen ratings system .
